      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software quality assurance procedures documented and version-controlled at Gradation 2.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 19.2) is a commercially validated code with documented QA procedures. Version control logs and regression test suite results were reviewed and confirmed compliant with MRL 2 requirements."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
